Name: Dark Box
About the game: You wake up on an island trying to remember your identity. The only thing you can do is: explore the island, and try to solve the puzzles one by one, leading to the ultimate truth. Black Box is a single-player game that expands 5 new mechanisms based on Sokoban. Featuring 6 chapters and 46 well-designed puzzles. You can contact us in the following ways Discord: Dark Box
